{"tid":2288270,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"日本上季GDP初值按季年率增長21.4%","createTime":"2020-11-16T11:19:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-16T13:51:17.000Z","uid":75656,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"0fffff3dad5df52fc4a41dd265055a774760b128","tid":2288270,"uid":75656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T11:19:17.000Z","msg":"日本第3季實質國內生產總值(GDP)初值按季增長5%，按季以年率計增長21.4%，兩者都好過市場預期，反映正擺脫新型肺炎疫情帶來的衝擊。<br />\n<br />\n期內，消費按季增長4.7%，資本開支按季下跌3.4%，兩者都差過預期，不過出口按季上升7%，令外部需求對GDP貢獻達到2.9個百分點。<br />\n<br />\n日本政府表示，上季經濟是4季以來首次增長，GDP及消費都創1980年有可比數據以來最快增速，外出用餐、休閑及汽車消費都有增長。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1560171-20201116.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1560171-20201116.htm&d=Mbax9TUBBsNKvtRo7%2B5fu%2FjlBAU1VhUdv3lOLHlSYeE%3D&h=22a2c1ad\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1560171-20201116.htm&h=a4c24b32\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1560171-20201116.htm</a>"},{"pid":"11ebd6da3e45b4fa5e752c17f21c8f8f7c39ad12","tid":2288270,"uid":199670,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T11:20:10.000Z","msg":"香港人：我要防疫啊 快啲關晒啲舖頭封鎖晒全港<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6357319cfc47fb3a7cd2f10b73780202ce60cd52","tid":2288270,"uid":109923,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T11:22:41.000Z","msg":"恐懼撚：好驚呀，死人啦"},{"pid":"077df5282855558181119d6d8da736100d9f64c6","tid":2288270,"uid":110562,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T11:23:00.000Z","msg":"旅行業